<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Banff Trail</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">Named after a beautiful town in Scotland called Banffshire, the Banff Trail is a calm and idyllic residential neighborhood in North West Calgary. </p>

            <p class="par-lg">Located to the north-east of the Trans- Canada Highway and Crowchild Trail intersection,
                the Banff Trail is located just a stoneâ€™s throw away from the University of Calgary and the McMahon
                Stadium to the west.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community in Banff Trail has been developed as per an Area Development Plan and is
                highly desirable among homebuyers from all walks of life including families, students, professionals and
                teachers alike. </p>

